					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Really they're the same thing. How big are the checkers, and how sharply can one pattern of checkers transition into another pattern of checkers? That could be considered a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spatial_frequency" class="postlink">spatial frequency</a> of sorts.
<br />
<br />Factoid: The checkers themselves can be used to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colour_recovery" class="postlink">recover color</a> from black-and-white film recordings of TV series such as <em>Doctor Who</em>.</div>

